{"tid":2421584,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（迷雲系）心目中最強同最廢阿妓陣容","createTime":"2021-02-24T15:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T08:06:26.000Z","uid":234212,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"cad766b24a85fab5b8500a851441fca985cbb1be","tid":2421584,"uid":234212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:05:24.000Z","msg":"係爺爺時期於一陣上陣過既球員<br />\n<br />\n最強陣容<br />\n龍門我鍾意Leno, 不過已經係後爺爺時代。中場用卡叔感覺穩過法比仔。前鋒唸過拉後亨利，用安歷卡代Bergkamp。左邊好多人選，overmas 同reyes（rip)我都鍾意<br />\n<br />\nGK: Szczesny<br />\nLB: Ashley Cole<br />\nCB: Campbell<br />\nCB: Toure<br />\nRB: Sagna <br />\nCDM:Vieria<br />\nCDM:Cazorla<br />\nLM: Pires<br />\nRM:Ljungberg<br />\nCF: Bergkamp<br />\nST:Henry<br />\n<br />\n最廢陣容<br />\n中堅太多人選，仲有Cygan😂左右中場好難選，選佐成日失機既2位。前面最廢一定唔係賓特拿，個查馬克個頹樣都唔開胃<br />\n<br />\nGK:Manninger<br />\nLB: Jenkinson<br />\nCB: Stepanovs<br />\nCB: Senderos <br />\nRB:Luzhny <br />\nCDM: Denilson <br />\nCDM: Coquelin<br />\nLM: Gervinho<br />\nRM: Wiltord <br />\nCF: Chamakh<br />\nST: Jeffers"},{"pid":"54de9152726dd12a275a859a09decf840a064c0b","tid":2421584,"uid":50745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:09:34.000Z","msg":"😂"},{"pid":"4fee061d1436f6eccab2a2c2ed99541e8d83d267","tid":2421584,"uid":8636,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"最強咪 不敗果年囉 仲使再諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0abcb8d27dcf856f3e7a6027a46a401d1c35f94d","tid":2421584,"uid":84013,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:18:52.000Z","msg":"n賓都無已經唔洗討論落去"},{"pid":"9fe495c4cdf8498247f956777c05b892e7aaaa23","tid":2421584,"uid":234509,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:20:03.000Z","msg":"高基連唔算廢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74ec015dc386e12583d29d81a411ccf4b89591f","tid":2421584,"uid":234212,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4fee